data.text: @cobuspienaar THE MESSAGE WITH ACTION 'HTTP://TEMPURI.ORG/ICOURTWORKSSERVICE/ADMIN_CAPTURING_SELECT_COURT' CANNOT BE PROCESSED AT THE RECEIVER, DUE TO A CONTRACTFILTER MISMATCH AT THE ENDPOINTDISPATCHER. THIS MAY BE BECAUSE OF EITHER A CONTRACT MISMATCH (MISMATCHED ACTIONS BETWEEN SENDER AND RECEIVER) OR A BINDING/SECURITY MISMATCH BETWEEN THE SENDER AND THE RECEIVER.  CHECK THAT SENDER AND RECEIVER HAVE THE SAME CONTRACT AND THE SAME BINDING (INCLUDING SECURITY REQUIREMENTS, E.G. MESSAGE, TRANSPORT, NONE).
